{
  "stem": "9898.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was a military commander of the whole area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I gave it to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Boy!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He says, we are here to teach them democracy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, whom, these killers and gangsters?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You're going to kill-- you're going to teach them democracy?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Forget it!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Not this generation.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we need this and this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We needed this and this, and I had to get it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, please calm down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do me a favor, he says to me, you know, behind the desk he was sitting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you need anything, come to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You will get anything what you wanted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But please come to me, and I'll get it for you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "OK, fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There, I saw the first game of baseball.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The boys were playing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he was teaching me, the captain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "His name was Captain-- see, I remember-- Captain [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Shapiro ?] from Chicago.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And after a few weeks, they closed it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they moved all the sick ones to Amberg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This was a Middle, Middle-Ages town which was-- city-- which was not touched by the American bombers because it was a beautiful city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was in charge of one hospital for people to recuperate from the concentration camps and from the POWs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was also-- there was a Jewish community there, a small Jewish community, but only from DPs, displaced person, and a rabbi there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I became the, the physician, the doctor of the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And after a few months, the Americans decided they have to have a big hospital for displaced person tuberculosis patients.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we organized a 500-bed hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And for the time, I was director of the hospital-- 500-bed tuberculosis hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then another one came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
